Simple fuel manager script for your ships. Edit the blocks custom data to change configuration

AutoFillBatteries - sets batteries to recharge when ship is docked
AutoFillHydrogen - sets hydrogen tanks to fill when ship is docked
AutoFillOxygen - sets hydrogen tanks to fill when ship is docked
AutoFillIce - Fills containers that have "IceStorage" in their name with ice when ship is docked
AutoCancelDampeners - Stops inertia dampeners when ship is docked
AutoPowerGen - starts H2 generators and reactors when power drops below set value (default is .2, edit config in code)